Divine Shrines

Shrines are places where divine patronage becomes visible in the world. At a
shrine you may pray or tithe, and shrine visits can also advance a pilgrimage.

Commands:

  pray at shrine
  tithe <amount> at shrine
  look shrine
  patron pilgrimage status

Shrines can currently be found at:

  Mitra  The Temple of Mitra in DarkWind City.
  Gaea   The rose garden near the chapel.
  Set    The black altar in the temple of Qazaash.

